\begin_inset Formula $t$
\end_inset 

 at 
\begin_inset Formula $m$
\end_inset 

.
 The union 
\begin_inset Formula $C_{(n,s)}\cup C_{(m,t)}$
\end_inset 

 is as above, with 
\emph on 
OR
\emph default 
 taking the place of 
\emph on 
AND
\emph default 
.
\layout Standard

Let the two letters that occur in the string be 
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset 

